---
theme: default
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Alice
    participant B as Bob
    participant C as Carol
    Note right of A: Request starts here
    A->>B: sendRequest()
    Note over A,B: Handshake phase
    B->>C: forward(data)
    Note left of C: Data arrives
        second line
    C-->>B: ack
    B-->>A: response
    Note over B: Processing complete
